@startuml sequence_notif
!theme plain
title Notification Center

participant "Mutator Handler" as MH
participant "Notifications.Persist" as P
database "DB" as DB
participant "TeamHub" as Hub
actor "User B" as B
participant "NotificationCenter" as NC
participant "NotificationsController" as C
participant "Handler" as H

MH -> P: Persist + Broadcast envelope
P -> DB: INSERT Notification per team member (except actor)
P -> Hub: SendAsync("eventName", {eventType, entityId, actorId, timestamp})
Hub --> NC: live event envelope
NC -> NC: badge++
B -> NC: open
NC -> C: GET /api/notifications
C -> H: ListNotificationsQuery
H -> DB: SELECT latest 50 WHERE UserId=B
H --> C: rows + unreadCount
C --> NC: 200
B -> NC: click item
NC -> C: POST /api/notifications/{id}/read
C -> H: MarkReadCommand
H -> DB: UPDATE ReadAt=now
NC --> B: navigate to entity
@enduml
